 Semantics
 ---------
 YellowLED indicates radio status: when its on the radio is on
 RedLED: toggles when sendnig a message
GreenLED: toggles when receiving a message
 Coordination between nodes:
 1) Nodes stay on until hear initial time-synch message from
   cluster-head
 2) When time-synch timer fires, then they expect to hear a
   ts message from the cluster-head or they stay on

